column1: Congratulations to Rusty Grills on your great victory! Looking forward to working with you to serve West Tennessee. #TNH77
Election day is today! Don't forget to get out and cast your vote for Rusty Grills as your next State Representative for District 77! #TNH77
Early voting ends on December 14th! Don't forget to cast your vote for Rusty Grills. He is going to make a great State Representative for #TNH77
Congratulations to Rusty Grills on your impressive primary win last night! Looking forward to a big general win in December!
Congratulations to @Mayorbwbeasley on last night’s victory! Looking forward to working with you!

The do-nothing Democrats’ secretive and illegitimate impeachment inquiry is a time suck! Meanwhile @realdonaldtrump is working for the American people and our economy is stronger than ever. https://t.co/3Awq5nAExS

Great evening at Carroll Co. GOP’s Pasta & Politics. Thanks to Col. Harding & his wife for hosting this event. I always enjoy speaking w/ W TN Republicans about re-electing @realDonaldTrump & taking back the House. I appreciate Carroll Co GOP Chair Brent Bradberry for the invite! https://t.co/siNluHbBHU

Great time speaking w/ folks at the Shelby Co. Republican Women Lunch. Thanks to Arla Pribnow for your work to make this event a success. It was great to see @TNFRW President @bbtbabs there. Looking forward to working w/ these conservative women to get @realDonaldTrump re-elected https://t.co/3FqOAi4RmT

Tonight @realDonaldTrump formally announced his bid for re-election! Thanks to his leadership we’ve seen 6 million new jobs created 2 conservative Supreme Court Justices confirmed and the wall is being built. I look forward to making sure he is re-elected in 2020! #Trump2020 https://t.co/CjCbEMfLJY
